                       |BKB-= |CKBEnter Message |BKB=-
               
|MKOEmess is the command used to change your entrance message that
only thieves will see when you log into Darkwind. Emess followed
by no value will reset your entrance message to the standard
message. Emess <message> will set your entrance message correctly.
Placing a $N in the message will put your name into the entrance
message, just as it does when setting your title when you advance
a level.

|CKOGLVL required: |GKB1
|CKOSyntax: |YKOemess <message>                |CKOCost: |WKOFree
